title: Weed Dr. Sanjay Gupta Reports WS.XviD-err0001 (CNN)
description:
Weed: Dr. Sanjay Gupta Presents (CNN)

Dr. Sanjay Gupta (CNN's chief medical correspondent and also a neurosurgeon) cuts through the smoke and travels around the world to uncover the highs and lows of marijuana.

Several people suffering from serious medical conditions are shown being dramatically helped by marijuana. Aspects covered include THC vs CBD, addiction, overdose risks of marijuana compared to other drugs, the effects on brain development in young people, driving while stoned, research being done in Israel, roadblocks to research in the United States etc.

This aired on CNN HD in Canada on Aug 11, 2013. Like all of my releases to date, the source is an analog rip, so the quality is, at best, something like A8 V8.
